Technical description:
table:table-cell is converted to w:tc
Based on style:table-cell-properties of the table style name the following properties have been converted :
w:tc/w:tcBorders children w:top, w:bottom, w:left, w:right have their attributes @w:val set to 'single'
@w:color set to substring-after(style:table-cell-properties/@fo:border, '#') and  
@w:sz set to substring-before(style:table-cell-properties/@fo:border, ' ')
